// ============non-terminal types=============
//  # => Integer
//  <assign> => Statement
//  <case> => Statement
//  <case>* => List<Statement>
//  <class decl> => ClassDecl
//  <class decl>+ => List<ClassDecl>
//  <decl in class> => Decl
//  <decl in class>* => List<Decl>
//  <empty bracket pair> => Object
//  <empty bracket pair>* => List<Object>
//  <empty bracket pair>** => List<Object>
//  <exp1> => Exp
//  <exp2> => Exp
//  <exp3> => Exp
//  <exp4> => Exp
//  <exp5> => Exp
//  <exp6> => Exp
//  <exp7> => Exp
//  <exp8> => Exp
//  <exp> => Exp
//  <expList> => ExpList
//  <formalList> => VarDeclList
//  <inst var decl> => Decl
//  <listElement> => VarDecl
//  <listElement>* => List<VarDecl>
//  <local var decl> => Statement
//  <method decl> => Decl
//  <next exp> => Exp
//  <next exp>* => List<Exp>
//  <program> => Program
//  <returnStmt> => Exp
//  <start> => void
//  <stmt> => Statement
//  <stmt>* => List<Statement>
//  <type> => Type
//  CHARLIT => Integer
//  ID => String
//  INTLIT => Integer
//  STRINGLIT => String
//  `! => void
//  `!= => void
//  `% => void
//  `&& => void
//  `( => void
//  `) => void
//  `* => void
//  `+ => void
//  `++ => void
//  `, => void
//  `- => void
//  `-- => void
//  `. => void
//  `/ => void
//  `: => void
//  `; => void
//  `< => void
//  `<= => void
//  `= => void
//  `== => void
//  `> => void
//  `>= => void
//  `[ => void
//  `] => void
//  `abstract => void
//  `assert => void
//  `boolean => void
//  `break => void
//  `byte => void
//  `case => void
//  `catch => void
//  `char => void
//  `class => void
//  `const => void
//  `continue => void
//  `default => void
//  `do => void
//  `double => void
//  `else => void
//  `enum => void
//  `extends => void
//  `false => void
//  `final => void
//  `finally => void
//  `float => void
//  `for => void
//  `goto => void
//  `if => void
//  `implements => void
//  `import => void
//  `instanceof => void
//  `int => void
//  `interface => void
//  `long => void
//  `native => void
//  `new => void
//  `null => void
//  `package => void
//  `private => void
//  `protected => void
//  `public => void
//  `return => void
//  `short => void
//  `static => void
//  `strictfp => void
//  `super => void
//  `switch => void
//  `synchronized => void
//  `this => void
//  `throw => void
//  `throws => void
//  `transient => void
//  `true => void
//  `try => void
//  `void => void
//  `volatile => void
//  `while => void
//  `{ => void
//  `|| => void
//  `} => void
//  any => Character
//  any* => List<Character>
//  any128 => Character
//  digit => Character
//  digit* => List<Character>
//  digit128 => Character
//  hexDigit => Character
//  hexDigit* => List<Character>
//  hexDigit128 => Character
//  idChar => Character
//  idChar* => List<Character>
//  idChar128 => Character
//  letter => Character
//  letter128 => Character
//  registerNewline => void
//  ws => void
//  ws* => void
// ============productions (after empty-removal)=============
// 0: $$start ::= <start>
// 1: <start> ::= ws* <program>
// 2: <start> ::= <program>
// 3: <program> ::= <class decl>+
// 4: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 5: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ `}
// 6: <class decl> ::= `class ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 7: <class decl> ::= `class ID `extends ID `{ `}
// 8: <decl in class> ::= <method decl>
// 9: <decl in class> ::= <inst var decl>
// 10: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID `( `) `{ <stmt>* `}
// 11: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID `( `) `{ `}
// 12: <type> ::= `int
// 13: <type> ::= `boolean
// 14: <type> ::= `void
// 15: <type> ::= `null
// 16: <type> ::= ID
// 17: <type> ::= <type> <empty bracket pair>
// 18: <empty bracket pair> ::= `[ `]
// 19: <stmt> ::= `{ <stmt>* `}
// 20: <stmt> ::= `{ `}
// 21: <stmt> ::= <assign> `;
// 22: <stmt> ::= <local var decl> `;
// 23: <stmt> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> !`else
// 24: <stmt> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> `else <stmt>
// 25: <stmt> ::= `for `( <assign> `; <exp> `; <assign> `) <stmt>
// 26: <stmt> ::= `for `( <assign> `; `; <assign> `) <stmt>
// 27: <stmt> ::= `while `( <exp> `) <stmt>
// 28: <stmt> ::= `break `;
// 29: <assign> ::= <exp> `= <exp>
// 30: <assign> ::= ID `++
// 31: <assign> ::= `++ ID
// 32: <assign> ::= ID `--
// 33: <assign> ::= `-- ID
// 34: <local var decl> ::= <type> ID `= <exp>
// 35: <inst var decl> ::= <type> ID `;
// 36: <stmt> ::= `;
// 37: <stmt> ::= `switch `( <exp> `) `{ <case>* `}
// 38: <stmt> ::= `switch `( <exp> `) `{ `}
// 39: <case> ::= `case <exp> `;
// 40: <exp> ::= <exp8>
// 41: <exp8> ::= <exp7>
// 42: <exp7> ::= <exp6>
// 43: <exp6> ::= <exp5>
// 44: <exp5> ::= <exp4>
// 45: <exp4> ::= <exp3>
// 46: <exp3> ::= <exp2>
// 47: <exp2> ::= <exp1>
// 48: <exp8> ::= <exp8> `|| <exp7>
// 49: <exp7> ::= <exp7> `&& <exp6>
// 50: <exp6> ::= <exp6> `== <exp5>
// 51: <exp6> ::= <exp6> `!= <exp5>
// 52: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `< <exp4>
// 53: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `<= <exp4>
// 54: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `> <exp4>
// 55: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `+ <exp3>
// 56: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `- <exp3>
// 57: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `* <exp2>
// 58: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `/ <exp2>
// 59: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `% <exp2>
// 60: <exp2> ::= `( <type> `) <exp1>
// 61: <exp2> ::= `+ <exp1>
// 62: <exp2> ::= `- <exp1>
// 63: <exp2> ::= `! <exp1>
// 64: <exp1> ::= ID
// 65: <exp1> ::= <exp1> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `]
// 66: <exp1> ::= INTLIT
// 67: <exp1> ::= STRINGLIT
// 68: <exp1> ::= CHARLIT
// 69: <exp1> ::= <exp1> `. ID
// 70: <exp1> ::= `this
// 71: <exp1> ::= `true
// 72: <exp1> ::= `false
// 73: <exp1> ::= `null
// 74: <exp1> ::= `new ID `( `)
// 75: <exp1> ::= `new <type> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `] <empty bracket pair>**
// 76: <exp1> ::= `new <type> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `] !<empty bracket pair>
// 77: letter ::= {"A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 78: letter128 ::= {193..218 225..250}
// 79: digit ::= {"0".."9"}
// 80: digit128 ::= {176..185}
// 81: any ::= {0..127}
// 82: any128 ::= {128..255}
// 83: ws ::= " "
// 84: ws ::= {10}
// 85: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o" ws*
// 86: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o"
// 87: `class ::= "#" "c" "l" ws*
// 88: `class ::= "#" "c" "l"
// 89: `extends ::= "#" "e" "x" ws*
// 90: `extends ::= "#" "e" "x"
// 91: `void ::= "#" "v" "o" ws*
// 92: `void ::= "#" "v" "o"
// 93: `int ::= "#" "i" "t" ws*
// 94: `int ::= "#" "i" "t"
// 95: `while ::= "#" "w" "h" ws*
// 96: `while ::= "#" "w" "h"
// 97: `if ::= "#" "+" ws*
// 98: `if ::= "#" "+"
// 99: `else ::= "#" "e" "l" ws*
// 100: `else ::= "#" "e" "l"
// 101: `for ::= "#" "f" "o" ws*
// 102: `for ::= "#" "f" "o"
// 103: `break ::= "#" "b" "r" ws*
// 104: `break ::= "#" "b" "r"
// 105: `this ::= "#" "t" "h" ws*
// 106: `this ::= "#" "t" "h"
// 107: `false ::= "#" "f" "a" ws*
// 108: `false ::= "#" "f" "a"
// 109: `true ::= "#" "t" "r" ws*
// 110: `true ::= "#" "t" "r"
// 111: `null ::= "#" "n" "u" ws*
// 112: `null ::= "#" "n" "u"
// 113: `new ::= "#" "n" "e" ws*
// 114: `new ::= "#" "n" "e"
// 115: `case ::= "#" "c" "e" ws*
// 116: `case ::= "#" "c" "e"
// 117: `public ::= "#" "p" "u" ws*
// 118: `public ::= "#" "p" "u"
// 119: `switch ::= "#" "s" "w" ws*
// 120: `switch ::= "#" "s" "w"
// 121: `! ::= "!" ws*
// 122: `! ::= "!"
// 123: `!= ::= "@" "!" ws*
// 124: `!= ::= "@" "!"
// 125: `% ::= "%" ws*
// 126: `% ::= "%"
// 127: `&& ::= "@" "&" ws*
// 128: `&& ::= "@" "&"
// 129: `* ::= "*" ws*
// 130: `* ::= "*"
// 131: `( ::= "(" ws*
// 132: `( ::= "("
// 133: `) ::= ")" ws*
// 134: `) ::= ")"
// 135: `{ ::= "{" ws*
// 136: `{ ::= "{"
// 137: `} ::= "}" ws*
// 138: `} ::= "}"
// 139: `- ::= "-" ws*
// 140: `- ::= "-"
// 141: `+ ::= "+" ws*
// 142: `+ ::= "+"
// 143: `= ::= "=" ws*
// 144: `= ::= "="
// 145: `== ::= "@" "=" ws*
// 146: `== ::= "@" "="
// 147: `[ ::= "[" ws*
// 148: `[ ::= "["
// 149: `] ::= "]" ws*
// 150: `] ::= "]"
// 151: `|| ::= "@" "|" ws*
// 152: `|| ::= "@" "|"
// 153: `< ::= "<" ws*
// 154: `< ::= "<"
// 155: `<= ::= "@" "<" ws*
// 156: `<= ::= "@" "<"
// 157: `> ::= ">" !"=" ws*
// 158: `> ::= ">" !"="
// 159: `. ::= "." ws*
// 160: `. ::= "."
// 161: `; ::= ";" ws*
// 162: `; ::= ";"
// 163: `++ ::= "@" "+" ws*
// 164: `++ ::= "@" "+"
// 165: `-- ::= "@" "-" ws*
// 166: `-- ::= "@" "-"
// 167: `/ ::= "/" ws*
// 168: `/ ::= "/"
// 169: ID ::= letter128 ws*
// 170: ID ::= letter128
// 171: ID ::= letter idChar* $$0
// 172: ID ::= letter $$0
// 173: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} digit* $$1
// 174: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} $$1
// 175: INTLIT ::= digit128 ws*
// 176: INTLIT ::= digit128
// 177: INTLIT ::= "0" hexDigit* $$2
// 178: INTLIT ::= "0" $$2
// 179: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"' ws*
// 180: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"'
// 181: STRINGLIT ::= '"' any* $$3
// 182: STRINGLIT ::= '"' $$3
// 183: CHARLIT ::= "'" any ws*
// 184: CHARLIT ::= "'" any
// 185: idChar ::= letter
// 186: idChar ::= digit
// 187: idChar ::= "_"
// 188: idChar128 ::= letter128
// 189: idChar128 ::= digit128
// 190: idChar128 ::= {223}
// 191: hexDigit ::= {"0".."9" "A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 192: hexDigit128 ::= {176..185 193..198 225..230}
// 193: digit* ::= digit* digit
// 194: digit* ::= digit
// 195: any* ::= any* any
// 196: any* ::= any
// 197: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>* <decl in class>
// 198: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>
// 199: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit* hexDigit
// 200: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit
// 201: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>* <stmt>
// 202: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>
// 203: <case>* ::= <case>* <case>
// 204: <case>* ::= <case>
// 205: idChar* ::= idChar* idChar
// 206: idChar* ::= idChar
// 207: <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>
// 208: <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>+ <class decl>
// 209: <empty bracket pair>** ::= <empty bracket pair>* !<empty bracket pair>
// 210: ws* ::= ws* ws
// 211: ws* ::= ws
// 212: <empty bracket pair>* ::= <empty bracket pair>* <empty bracket pair>
// 213: <empty bracket pair>* ::= <empty bracket pair>
// 214: $$0 ::= idChar128 ws*
// 215: $$0 ::= idChar128
// 216: $$1 ::= digit128 ws*
// 217: $$1 ::= digit128
// 218: $$2 ::= hexDigit128 ws*
// 219: $$2 ::= hexDigit128
// 220: $$3 ::= any128 ws*
// 221: $$3 ::= any128

**** STATE 0 ****
    $$start ::= <%> <start> // $
    -----------------------
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // <class decl>
    <program> ::= [#] <%> <class decl>+ // $
    <start> ::= <%> ws* <program> // $
    <start> ::= [ws*] <%> <program> // $
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" [ws*] // ID
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" ws* // ID
    ws ::= <%> " " // <program>
    ws ::= <%> " " // ws
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // <program>
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // ws
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // <program>
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // ws
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // <program>
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // ws
        <class decl>+ => shift: 72
        "#" => shift: 605
        ws => shift: 440
        <program> => shift: 623
        `class => shift: 438
        <start> => shift: 562
        ws* => shift: 317
        {10} => shift: 31
        " " => shift: 104
        <class decl> => shift: 552
**** STATE 1 ****
    -----------------------
**** STATE 2 ****
    `. ::= "." <%> ws* // ID
    `. ::= "." [ws*] <%> // ID
    -----------------------
    ws ::= <%> " " // ID
    ws ::= <%> " " // ws
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // ID
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // ws
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // ID
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // ws
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // ID
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // ws
        {199..218 231..250} => reduce: 160
        "w" => reduce: 160
        "u" => reduce: 160
        "s" => reduce: 160
        "o" => reduce: 160
        "i" => reduce: 160
        "e" => reduce: 160
        "c" => reduce: 160
        "a" => reduce: 160
        " " => shift: 104
        ws* => shift: 34
        {"A".."Z" "d" "g" "j".."k" "m" "q" "y".."z"} => reduce: 160
        ws => shift: 440
        {10} => shift: 31
        {193..198 225..230} => reduce: 160

        "v" => reduce: 160
        "t" => reduce: 160

        "b" => reduce: 160
        ID => reduce: 160
**** STATE 3 ****
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `!=
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `%
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `&&
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `)

    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `==
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `>
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `[
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `]
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `||
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // <empty bracket pair>**
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // ID
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `!=
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `%
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `&&
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `(
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `)
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `*
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `+
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `++
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `-
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `--
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `.
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `/

**** STATE 314 ****
    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* <%> `} // $
    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* <%> `} // <class decl>
    <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>* <%> <decl in class> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>* <%> <decl in class> // `}
    -----------------------
    <decl in class> ::= <%> <inst var decl> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class> ::= <%> <inst var decl> // `}
    <decl in class> ::= <%> <method decl> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class> ::= <%> <method decl> // `}
    <inst var decl> ::= <%> <type> [#] ID `; // <decl in class>
    <inst var decl> ::= <%> <type> [#] ID `; // `}
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID `( `) `{ <stmt>* `} // <decl in class>
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID `( `) `{ <stmt>* `} // `}
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID `( `) `{ [<stmt>*] `} // <decl in class>
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID `( `) `{ [<stmt>*] `} // `}
    <type> ::= [#] <%> <type> <empty bracket pair> // <empty bracket pair>
    <type> ::= [#] <%> <type> <empty bracket pair> // ID
    <type> ::= [#] <%> ID // <empty bracket pair>
    <type> ::= [#] <%> ID // ID
    <type> ::= [#] <%> `boolean // <empty bracket pair>
    <type> ::= [#] <%> `boolean // ID
    <type> ::= [#] <%> `int // <empty bracket pair>
    <type> ::= [#] <%> `int // ID
    <type> ::= [#] <%> `null // <empty bracket pair>
    <type> ::= [#] <%> `null // ID
    <type> ::= [#] <%> `void // <empty bracket pair>
    <type> ::= [#] <%> `void // ID
    ID ::= <%> letter [idChar*] $$0 // <empty bracket pair>
    ID ::= <%> letter [idChar*] $$0 // ID

    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `!=
    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `%
    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `&&
    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `)
    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `*
    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `+
    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `-
    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `.
    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `/
    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `;
    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `<
    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `<=

    `++ ::= "@" "+" <%> ws* // `)
